    "description": "BikeDekho Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Digital Marketing Manager for our Vijayawada operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout BikeDekho Advisory Limited:\nBikeDekho Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BikeDekho Advisory Limited!",
